---
layout: base.njk
title: Deals & Discount Codes
description: Vetted products and services we actually use — with exclusive discount codes for the Paws Beyond Odds community.
pageClass: promotions
---

<div class="page-hero page-hero--amber">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">Community deals</div>
    <h1>Products we actually <em>use and trust</em></h1>
    <p>Every product listed here is something we've used or researched carefully. We only partner with brands whose products we'd recommend regardless of sponsorship. If we have a discount code for you, it means we've vetted it first.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="promos-transparency">
  <div class="transparency-inner">
    <div class="transparency-icon">📋</div>
    <div>
      <h2>How this page works</h2>
      <p>Some of these partnerships earn us a small commission or flat fee. That income helps keep the rest of this site free, ad-free, and maintained. We will always disclose when a listing is sponsored, and we will never list a product we don't stand behind. If you have a question about any listing, <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}">reach out</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% if sponsors.length > 1 %}

  {# Group by category #}
  {% set categories = {
    "food": "Food & Diet",
    "supplements": "Supplements",
    "equipment": "Equipment & Supplies",
    "services": "Services",
    "other": "Other"
  } %}

  {% for categoryKey, categoryLabel in categories %}
    {% set catSponsors = [] %}
    {% for sponsor in sponsors %}
      {% if sponsor.category == categoryKey %}
        {% set catSponsors = (catSponsors.push(sponsor), catSponsors) %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

    {% if catSponsors.length > 0 %}
    <section class="promos-category">
      <div class="promos-inner">
        <h2 class="promos-category-title">{{ categoryLabel }}</h2>
        <div class="promos-grid">
          {% for sponsor in sponsors %}
          {% if sponsor.category == categoryKey %}
          <div class="promo-card {% if sponsor.endorsed %}promo-endorsed{% endif %}">
            <div class="promo-header">
              {% if sponsor.logo %}
              <img src="{{ sponsor.logo }}" alt="{{ sponsor.name }} logo" class="promo-logo">
              {% else %}
              <div class="promo-logo-placeholder">{{ sponsor.name }}</div>
              {% endif %}
              {% if sponsor.endorsed %}
              <span class="promo-badge">✓ We use this</span>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="promo-body">
              <h3 class="promo-name">{{ sponsor.name }}</h3>
              <p class="promo-tagline">{{ sponsor.tagline }}</p>
              <p class="promo-desc">{{ sponsor.description }}</p>

              {% if sponsor.endorsement %}
              <blockquote class="promo-endorsement">{{ sponsor.endorsement }}</blockquote>
              {% endif %}

              {% if sponsor.conditions %}
              <div class="promo-conditions">
                {% for condition in sponsor.conditions %}
                <a href="{{ ('/conditions/' + condition + '/') | url }}" class="promo-condition-chip">{{ condition | upper }}</a>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="promo-footer">
              {% if sponsor.code %}
              <div class="promo-code-block">
                <span class="promo-code-label">Your discount code</span>
                <button class="promo-code" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('{{ sponsor.code }}'); this.textContent = 'Copied!';" title="Click to copy">
                  {{ sponsor.code }}
                </button>
                <span class="promo-discount">{{ sponsor.discount }}</span>
              </div>
              {% endif %}
              <a href="{{ sponsor.url }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">
                Visit {{ sponsor.name }} →
              </a>
              <p class="promo-disclosure">Sponsored listing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

{% else %}

<section class="promos-empty">
  <div class="promos-empty-inner">
    <span class="promos-empty-icon">🏷️</span>
    <h2>Deals and codes coming soon</h2>
    <p>We're building this out carefully — only listing products and services we'd actually recommend. Check back soon, or <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}">get in touch</a> if you're a brand interested in partnering.</p>
    <div class="promos-promise">
      <strong>Our promise:</strong> Every listing on this page will be something we've used or researched. No pay-to-play. No mystery partnerships. If it's here, it's because we think it genuinely helps cat owners.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% endif %}

<section class="promos-partner-cta">
  <div class="partner-inner">
    <h2>Are you a pet health brand?</h2>
    <p>We work with brands whose products are genuinely useful to cat owners managing chronic illness. If that's you, reach out — we're selective and we keep it honest.</p>
    <a href="mailto:hello@pawsbeyondodds.com" class="btn btn-outline">Get in touch →</a>
  </div>
</section>
